  "description": "Feed the need for speed with this 20-minute dinner. You'll pan-fry pork loin steak before serving with a creamy carrot and parsnip mash and garlicky spring greens. Smother the lot in homemade gravy and dig in. High in protein. Protein contributes to a growth in muscle mass.",
